messages.content:
🌈 Rainbow Color Explosion Build Challenge 🎆 

Rainbows are a magical phenomenon (well, it’s actually science!) that occur when light is reflected and bent through water. What results is an arc of colors, and everyone sees it differently! What does that have to do with this challenge? Not a whole lot (unless you decide to build a rainbow), but Minecraft Earth has colors too! And you’re going to use them!

**Use a variety of color items and blocks to build something fun and imaginative.** 

Make it big or make it small. Use a few color blocks or use them all. Whatever it is, bring a smile and color into our world! :party_wool: 

:timer: Challenge dates: October 7, 2020 – October 19, 2020 at 6 PM PT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! The challenge theme is open to interpretation.
:sign: Post images or a video __and__ buildplate link of your one (1) final submission in #rainbow-color-explosion-challenge by the end date. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges_og: Submissions may be featured in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!

🌈 *Somewhere over the rainbow…* are all of your majestic colorful builds! We challenged you to reach into your inventory of colored blocks to build something that’d make us smile. Prismatic tunnels, exploding volcanoes, and vibrant contraptions galore! Your :apartyblob: RAINBOWTASTIC :apartyblob1: builds surely delighted us all.

:challenges: The winners of the #rainbow-color-explosion-challenge are…
:diamond: @Frahst - My Rainbow Tree That Spreads Color Throughout
:gold: @-_-lol.ivan-_- - Colorful Greenhouse + Rainbow Library
:iron: @clovepod - Rainbow Color Testing and Research Laboratory
:iron_nugget: @Callum - Rainbow Sheep Statue

**Congratulations to the winners! And thank you to everyone who participated!** Submissions may be featured in social media posts. Checkout all the brilliant builds in the pinned messages. :party_wool:
